Modification notice (2026-07-14):

The upstream multi-style cover generator was reduced to a standalone Codex
Skill named wechat-sketch-cover. It has one warm hand-drawn notebook style,
one left-title/right-illustration composition, backend-agnostic candidate
generation, no preference file, no branding, and one final PNG size of
1923 x 818.

The fixed style specification was rewritten from the upstream warm palette,
hand-drawn rendering guidance, and cover workflow. The bundled OfferPilot
cover image was supplied by the repository owner with permission for public
redistribution under this repository's MIT License. It is used only as a QA
style reference and is never passed to the image-generation model.

LICENSE and NOTICE are copied into the installable Skill so attribution travels
with installation.
